('Dr. Höhne Law & Tax', 'Legal', 'International law and tax firm offering comprehensive legal and tax solutions to companies, start-ups, freelancers, and individuals in Barcelona and Costa Brava. As expats themselves, they understand the common issues and concerns that people living abroad face when needing legal services. Founded by Dr. Hans-Hellmut Höhne in 1976, with nearly 50 years of experience advising international clients in Spain. Services include tax law (Spanish and international taxation, double taxation treaties), real estate law (property purchase, sale, rental), inheritance law, family law (divorce, custody, alimony), corporate law (company formation, bylaws, shareholder matters), contract law, start-up law, and criminal law. Multilingual team speaks English, German, Spanish, Catalan, and French. Offers 100% online service for remote clients.', 'Ronda de General Mitre, 179-181', 'Barcelona', 'Barcelona', '+34 934 533 866', 'info@drhoehne.com', 'https://drhoehne.com', true, false, false, false, NOW(), NOW()),

